
# Configuration that is used for production build in Vercel

## App URLs
### Shared envs across all apps in Vercel shared envs
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEBAPP_URL="https://app.usebondery.com"
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEBSITE_URL="https://usebondery.com"
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL="https://api.usebondery.com"

## Supabase Configuration
### Unique envs per app/project
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL="https://<your-project-id>.supabase.co"
PUBLIC_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY="sb_publishable_<your-publishable-key>"
PRIVATE_SUPABASE_SECRET_KEY="sb_secret_<your-secret-key>"

## Analytics (optional)
### Shared envs across all apps in Vercel shared envs
DO_NOT_TRACK=true
NEXT_TELEMETRY_DISABLED=1

## Email Configuration (for feedback notifications)
### Unique envs per app/project
PRIVATE_EMAIL_HOST="smtp.example.com"
PRIVATE_EMAIL_PORT=465
PRIVATE_EMAIL_USER="username"
PRIVATE_EMAIL_PASS="your-email-password"
PRIVATE_EMAIL_ADDRESS="robot@usebondery.com"

## Maps / Geocoding (mapy.com)
### Shared envs across all apps in Vercel shared envs
PUBLIC_MAPS_URL="https://api.mapy.com"
PRIVATE_MAPS_KEY="<your-maps-api-key>"

## AI Chat
### Unique envs per app/project
PRIVATE_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY="sk-ant-<your-anthropic-api-key>"

## Polar.sh Payments
### Unique envs per app/project
# From: polar.sh → Settings → Webhooks → (your endpoint) → Signing Secret
PRIVATE_POLAR_WEBHOOK_SECRET="<your-polar-webhook-secret>"
PRIVATE_POLAR_ACCESS_TOKEN="<your-polar-access-token>"
PUBLIC_POLAR_ENVIRONMENT="production"
POLAR_PRODUCT_ID="<your-polar-product-id>"

## Rate limiting (optional, leave empty to use in-memory store)
### Unique envs per app/project
PRIVATE_REDIS_URL="rediss://:your-token@your-instance.upstash.io:6379"
